A '''Trandoshan holding cell''' was any type of [[Durasteel/Legends|durasteel]] holding cell made by the [[Trandoshan/Legends|Trandoshans]]. They were commonly used to hold captive [[Slavery/Legends|slaves]]. They had to be able to sustain massive damage, as [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]] were meant to be held in them.

